## 6. Next Implementation Phases

**Phase 1 - Alignment (2-3 hrs):** Map curriculum to CEFR, check vocab against DELF lists

**Phase 2 - Grammar Planning (4-5 hrs):** Write 52 grammar lessons (5-paragraph each)

**Phase 3 - Content Creation (15-20 hrs):** 
- 50 examples √ó 365 days = 18,250 items
- 50 quiz questions √ó 365 days = 18,250 items
- **Realistic:** Create Week 1 template, use AI-assisted generation + your review

**Phase 4 - Testing (5-10 hrs):** Pilot Week 1, run mock DELF A1, iterate

